This approch is in contrast to the current either/or model of take it or leave it for consent around for instance sharing data on apps. Our negotiation approach opens up new opportunities for businesses - it can increase opportunities for existing data or other information of relevance given these refinements.

We have also found that we can automate preference selections so that a system can learn these choices thus reducing bother to the person. Again this opens up new opportunities for business engagement around terms and conditions for instance to be more context specfic.</gtr:description><gtr:exploitationPathways>business - can use our tested interaction approach to inform business models.

